   - [CS73187]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;embryo-defective; embryos arrest at the 1 cell-embryo stage; immature silique of self-pollinated cyl2/+ plants exhibit two types of mutant seeds: numerous small brown seeds and rare large white seeds
   - [cyl2/+]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Segregates embryo lethals that arrest at early stages of embryogenesis. Also defective transmission through male and female gametophytes.
